title: World to conquer
subject_group: Advertising, Film, Journalism, Mass Media & TV/Home movies and video
abstract: A sci-fi set piece with DIY special effects.
description: This sci-fi 'Straford Brothers Specialite' is a scripted drama featuring local student actors. A classic sci-fi set up, it has some nifty DYI special effects including painstakingly made minature sets (watch out for the alien control room!), animated spaceship and a alien periscope very reminiscent of early 'Doctor Who' episodes.
